item.title: Help me to speak at SP24 the first SharePoint (web) conference all around the world!
item.description: Some great SharePoint MVP’s are organizing an amazing event on April the 16th/17th : the SP24. The idea is: Amazing speakers Amazing conferences All around the world 2 tracks 48 sessions A few thousands attendees 24 hours straight You even get to choose the sessions! And it’s free Translating SharePoint 2013 from beginning to ending Really motivated by this great concept I decided to apply for a conference.
